text: Lal wa Sarjangal, also called La'l Wa Sar Jangal or simply Lal, United States National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (لعل), is a town in and the administrative center of Lal wa Sarjangal District, Ghor Province, Afghanistan. ==See also== *Hazarajat ==Notes== Category:Populated places in Ghor Province Category:Hazarajat
title: Lal wa Sarjangal
